<item>
            <title>[SOLR-16731] &quot;tls&quot; key incorrect in SystemInfoHandler requests</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16731</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;SystemInfoHandler&lt;/tt&gt; tries to display if TLS is enabled or not for a cluster, but in order to do this it checks the cluster property &quot;base_url&quot;. This is not the right property to look at, should be &quot;urlScheme&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
